<figureCitation id="3CB12A1F832AFFA8FF20FF65FEEFFF3C" box="[222,303,151,177]" captionStart="FIGURES 25–32" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1920,1944]" captionTargetBox="[162,1417,191,1877]" captionTargetId="figure-28@16.[154,1434,181,1896]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 25–32.Adults of Manitischeria spp. 25, M. unca (Diškus &amp; Stonis), paratype; 26, M. tyrocnistis (Meyrick), lectotype (first documentation); 27, M. puplesisi (Kozlov), holotype (first documentation); 28, M. armata (Diškus &amp; Stonis), holotype; 29–32, M. brachiata Diškus &amp; Stonis, sp. nov., holotype" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4709312" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4709312/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="259">Fig. 27</figureCitation>
) and its male genitalia (
<figureCitation id="3CB12A1F832AFFA8FDC7FF65FD01FF3C" box="[569,705,150,177]" captionStart="FIGURES 58–62" captionStartId="22.[151,264,1922,1946]" captionTargetBox="[169,1422,200,1871]" captionTargetId="figure-28@22.[154,1434,181,1899]" captionTargetPageId="22" captionText="FIGURES 58–62. Male genitalia of Manitischeria puplesisi (Kozlov); 58, 59, holotype (first photographic documentation), slide no. 13837 (ZIN); 60, non-type specimen, slide no. AD1024 (ZIN), valvae; 61, 62, same, phallus and juxta" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4709335" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4709335/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="259">Figs. 58, 59</figureCitation>
